name: プロデューサー
trans: Are you listening to music, there?

No, just thought you
were listening to...

Sorry, I probably
intruded just now.

name: 透
text: え？　そんなことないよ

name: 透
text: ぼーっとしてただけだし
trans: I was just spacing out, that's all.

name: 透
trans: ──Is it okay if I keep listening to this?

name: プロデューサー
text: （うっ……しまった。別のことを言えば良かったな……）
trans: (Ah... I should've said something else instead...)
